371
00:31:38,284 --> 00:31:40,370
Orang pelik itu bukan manusia.

372
00:31:41,705 --> 00:31:43,164
Percayalah cakap saya.

373
00:31:43,248 --> 00:31:44,249
KEDAI MI UNNIE

